&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone to join our busy office within Cotswold House, Oxford, for 18.75 hours per week. You will provide timely, accurate and confidential administrative services to the Multidisciplinary Eating Disorders Team. We require someone to provide a consistent, professional, polite and well-informed front door service to any visitors to the Unit, as well as to provide support to medical staff and other colleagues within the Eating Disorders team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ideally we are looking for someone who is proficient in the working practices of the Unit including the Patient centred computer system, Carenotes, however training will be provided.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
